  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package binds a credibility claim that summarises the overall assessment conclusion; supporting evidence documents were reviewed during the assessment but the claim node itself carries no structured provenance link to any evidence artefact.",
